These files are included under `tests/fixtures/specs/` as reference
material. They are not redistributed with the compiled library.

Roles:
- `hancom_test.json`  — a runnable example spec used by integration
                        tests. Strict JSON, parses into `DvcSpec`.
- `hancom_full.json`  — a key catalog listing every field the
                        reference tool understands. NOT strict JSON
                        (missing inter-field commas, carries a
                        `[Json schema]` header marker) and not meant
                        to be loaded as a spec. Kept as a developer
                        reference for extending `DvcSpec`.
